Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.83,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,間違いない。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:45.75,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,これは...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:49.63,Sign,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H423B27&\fnImpact\move(640,15.126,640,92.269,0,2151)}陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:47.66,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,陰謀だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.27,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,そうだ、俺は...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:01.76,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,俺は大きな陰謀に...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:05.76,Background,Comment,0,0,0,,陰謀の...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:06.81,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,途轍もなく巨大な陰謀に...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:11.17,Background,Comment,0,0,0,,A dream and a conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:10.37,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,陰謀に...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:15.47,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,巻き込まれてしまったのだ!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:33.12,Background,Comment,0,0,0,,...magical girl, that is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.96,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,どうも（？）最近頭の調子は悪い...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:43.70,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,一日１６時間も寝ているからだろうか?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:52.58,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,隣の部屋から今日も美少女のアニメI can hear the theme song of a girlie anime blasting through from next door again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:56.01,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This has been going on every single day since last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.17,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I already know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.89,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that phrase hundreds of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:06.39,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But at any rate, I don't know about this "pururin" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:09.34,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Is she a bouncy-looking girl or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.13,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.74,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Or does it mean a girl that looks like a pudding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.24,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:31.81,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.58,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Today's the day! I'm not going to take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:46.55,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate this song! If I have to keep listening to it, I'm going to go crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.81,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to go complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.27,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.55,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,In fact, it's pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:58.03,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I just have to open the door and walk a few steps towards the next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.94,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And then I'd knock, open the door and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.36,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You frickin' anime otaku! Turn that shit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.99,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like that, I'd yell at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:08.87,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.48,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.71,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,There must be something wrong with that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:19.76,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.10,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Doesn't he have any sense of shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.80,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's just creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.34,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.39,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I just want him to stop walking around the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.89,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Eeeew! What a freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:34.98,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.98,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.98,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That was my first summer in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:45.94,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I was on my way to school and it was scorching hot outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:06:01.34,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I ran back to my apartment as if I were running away from it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:07.73,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And from that day forward, I stopped going outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.88,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome to Garden Mania.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.98,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Today we're going to talk about goldenrod.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:43.75,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:45.56,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:46.79,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:47.84,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:54.35,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:07:00.07,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy... Conspiracy... Conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:08.90,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.56,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,There are conspiracies in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:16.19,Background2,Comment,0,0,1,,The Columbia disaster was a Venusian conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:16.69,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right, she was saying the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:18.63,Background2,Comment,0,0,1,,Brown-dyed hair is the beauty industry's conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:21.44,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right, the existence of conspiracy is talked about in society as if it were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:21.44,Background2,Comment,0,0,1,,Cedar pollen is the facial tissue industry's conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:27.93,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Ninety-nine percent of all so-called "conspiracies" are simply imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.73,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Or they're just big intentional lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Basically, they're a bunch of baloney.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:35.47,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So one percent of it is the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:39.01,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw a junior student being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:40.84,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,He was a student from the middle school division.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:44.87,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I wanted to show off in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:46.23,Background2,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.71,Background2,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy... Conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.99,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me something, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:55.51,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of conspiracy too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.04,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:02.00,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Homeroom isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:03.60,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Quiet please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.83,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the noisiest one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:06.84,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:09.84,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,If you have something to say, raise your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.84,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Was that a conspiracy too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.87,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a conspiracy too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:17.63,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This is too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:18.94,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This is too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:20.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This is too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:21.88,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This is too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:22.98,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This is too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:26.30,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Are they all conspiracies?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:34.44,Background,Comment,0,0,0,,A dream and a conspiracy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:39.34,Background,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,3000)\org(0,0)}Magical girl
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:42.29,Background,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.29,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:48.06,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I must've gotten myself involved in a real, less than one percent probable, conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.85,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.05,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So you finally realized, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:54.93,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.59,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Things continuously going wrong for you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:09:01.30,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,was in fact a conspiracy to make you withdraw from society!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.74,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But who would plot a conspiracy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:08.46,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Conspiracy radio waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.58,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.70,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the N.H.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.63,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That evil secret organization N.H.K. is attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.85,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,N.H.K.?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.83,Sign,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(640,689.747)\fnSegoe Print\c&HAF9A87&\b1}Animated by Nakajima SHIGEO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.67,Note,Comment,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Metamorphic Magical Girl Pururin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:26.67,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:31.38,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Why didn't I realize such a simple thing until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:40.09,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't talk about anime without mentioning otaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.11,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And otaku tend to be anti-social.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.96,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,People like that eventually become reclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:48.90,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:54.08,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,they have been mass-producing anime otaku by showing them interesting anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:57.66,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,helping to create a massive emergence of NEETs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.37,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Basically, N.H.K. is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:03.70,Note,Comment,0,0,0,,JAPAN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:04.83,Note,Comment,0,0,0,,SOCIAL-WITHDRAWAL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:05.96,Note,Comment,0,0,0,,ASSOCIATION
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:06.92,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Nihon {\alpha&HFF&}Hikikomori Kyokai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:07.65,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Nihon Hikikomori {\alpha&HFF}Kyokai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:08.42,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Nihon Hikikomori Kyokai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:17.10,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the man who became aware of the N.H.K.'s conspiracy:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.31,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato Tatsuhiro, 22 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.58,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've shut myself away from society for three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:25.02,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Almost four years now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:30.40,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Some karate masters would seclude themselves in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.94,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,in order to master the secret technique that could break rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.38,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,If I can obtain strength by secluding myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:42.08,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I should have cultivated enough strength to crush this beer bottle by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:48.61,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Who broke the beer bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.48,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.79,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It hurts! It hurts! It hurts! Where's the first aid kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:58.40,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.43,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, before that, I'd better do something about these shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.42,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:06.53,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,First I have to clean up the shards, then treat this wound and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.40,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost! I'm too busy right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.83,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,First of all, I'm a NEET!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:14.34,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Why would a NEET randomly make an appearance anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:17.95,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, could it be the utility bill collector?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:20.45,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, I haven't sent them money for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.34,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,If they turn off my electricity,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:26.16,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't be able to live my NEET life comfortably anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:29.83,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.56,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.78,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Jeez, I know they heard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.80,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:46.66,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.63,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! I didn't know you were in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:23.43,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,We're sorry to bother you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:27.06,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.32,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Your face is bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:34.14,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.44,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:42.17,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, we've been distributing this pamphlet for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.74,Note,Comment,0,0,0,,The Time is Already Here!\NWake up! "Hikikomori" Special Report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.95,Note,Comment,0,0,0,,NEET Population on the Rise\NAre You Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:47.26,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's this month's special article.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:49.03,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard of NEETs before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:53.51,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's about the people who shut themselves away from society, refusing to go to school or work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:56.42,Background2,Comment,0,0,0,,It's become a serious social issue these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:59.06,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Does this lady know that I've been shutting myself away from society?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:04.10,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it possible that I'm a well-known NEET in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.22,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.68,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you be interested in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.29,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,If so, please take a look at it and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:16.70,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Me? A NEET?! Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:21.14,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, supposedly I haven't talked to anyone for almost a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.47,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I dropped out of the college because of my social withdrawal trait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.74,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And of course I'm unemployed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.47,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,To make matters worse, I have no hope for the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.86,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.52,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,"Are you okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.79,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Hell yeah, I'm okay, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.80,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:35.44,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:42.75,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,No one would go through this pain if a little prayer could fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:45.01,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,What can you possibly understand about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.24,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,when I can't understand a damn thing about it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:50.90,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You would never understand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.70,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Misaki! Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.68,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.40,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:38.19,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, I do know what I should be doing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:42.62,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I should get out there right now and find a part-time job or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:47.00,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And if I did that, that rumor about a NEET living in this room would be just a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:55.58,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Then, I'm sure that girl would think I just happened to be home because I was off today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.21,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:15.32,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got a handkerchief, pocket tissues, my wallet and my resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:29.58,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that you guys are hiring... I've heard that you guys are hiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.81,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that you guys are hiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.57,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that you guys are hiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.39,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that you guys are hiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.71,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that you guys are hiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.99,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that you guys are hiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:54.15,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that you guys are hiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:57.85,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that you guys are hiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:01.73,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that you guys are hiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:13.84,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that you guys are hiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:14.74,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.88,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:24.40,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've heard that... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:28.76,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.28,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:33.55,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:35.42,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.10,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,"I've heard that you..." What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.65,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:48.12,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You like motorcycles? I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.56,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You can become the wind, you know. There's nothing like the sound of that engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.37,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna go for a ride together? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:59.74,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But to tell you the truth, I've never even ridden a bike before! Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.24,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:02.83,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.96,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:16.18,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But I already know that I can't kill myself like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.76,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Because I'll just pass out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.10,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,and my grip will weaken before I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:27.32,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Why was she, of all girls, there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:33.12,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Should a servant of God be working a part-time job?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:39.41,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I guess even a servant of God needs money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.16,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, she's just flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.54,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right, she's flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.30,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I shouldn't! I shouldn't be doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.38,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:50.88,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I shouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.59,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,God is watching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:12.80,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:15.37,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,there's no way the utility company would actually send someone to my house
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:17.20,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,to collect outstanding bills from me nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:23.18,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,So, ignoring this won't affect my life in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:25.29,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,In fact, I should ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:29.29,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Because I carelessly opened the door yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.56,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I was... I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:52.94,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.07,Sign,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fnSegoe Print\pos(677.753,152.773)\frz11.632}RESUME ENCLOSED
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.40,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Did she come all the way to drop this off for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.63,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To Tatsuhiro Sato,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.89,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have been chosen for my project.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:17.69,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Therefore, please come to Mita Park on 4th Street at 9:00 tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.86,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Misaki Nakahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:26.44,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,If this is about soliciting me for her religion, she's not doing a good job at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:30.07,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe anyone would fall for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:33.19,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But at the same time, this is how they get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:37.08,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Using young girls to lure young men...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.70,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's an old trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:41.82,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,She must be a promiscuous girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.92,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Why would I fall for a girl like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.33,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.36,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Come to me, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.39,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:06.43,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please come to Mita Park on 4th Street at 9:00 tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:12.44,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, that park is the only place I can relax outside of this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:21.07,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,And I was thinking about going to the park to relax tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:31.01,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I shouldn't let some bizarre letter like that interfere with my schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.47,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:38.28,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I was already planning to go to the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:54.15,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I realized that I overlooked one big possibility in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:58.15,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,It's possible that the letter was just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:04.84,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I'm the biggest clown for being here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.94,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,What am I saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:12.64,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I was already planning to come here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.63,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you run away this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:25.46,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I was going to hire you right then and there because we've been short-staffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:29.47,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you get scared of going outside and working?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.22,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Since you're a hikikomori?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.51,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:38.74,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Because I know how to get you out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:39.23,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:43.48,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, I've known about you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:48.79,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I've come to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:56.00,Sign,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H06303B&\fs72.605\pos(731.685,134.621)}Project
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H473CB6&\pos(640,136.135)\fs60.504}Episode 01
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H2814CA&\pos(656.18,468.907)\fs60.504}Welcome to the Project!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.61,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Project!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:32.01,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,I mustn't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:33.17,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,This is Hitomi's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:35.68,Default,Comment,0,0,0,,You can write the script, can't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:40.03,Note,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HD49F3A&\pos(640,113.445)\fs60.504}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:40.03,Note,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HB27000&\pos(640,446.219)\fs60.504}Welcome to the Creator!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.18,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.26,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.31,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,as I turn my back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.64,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.81,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,"Where am I supposed to go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:32.86,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:42.20,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,In the shadows of a back alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:49.33,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the hands of a clock repaint the time that has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.07,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Extended hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.44,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,puzzle pieces that don't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.74,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.79,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,reunite with something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.42,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,that has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.96,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Recover
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.22,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the last piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:24.35,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,and let's start walking.
