Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:16.28,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1\fs50.4}Ababa, ababa, ababa, dancing baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:24.23,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1}When we were born naked,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.27,0:22:27.19,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an3}we were all loved equally, just as it's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:30.34,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1}But why, as life goes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:33.34,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an3}does each destiny take a different path? It's almost cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:36.24,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1}Some can look at other's eyes, while others can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:39.22,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1}Some get to learn love, while others don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:42.12,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1}If that's how it is, I'd rather be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:45.21,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an3}a baby, a baby human till I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:50.92,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1}"Oh, what an adorable baby!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:57.30,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1}"I just want to love you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:55.55,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an3\fs50.4\i1} (Just like I planned!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:57.30,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an3\fs50.4\i1} (It worked perfectly!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.41,0:23:00.18,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1}The baby she's holding isn't really a baby human.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:03.18,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1}"Ababa!" I snicker to myself, hiding in my pretended innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:06.15,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1\fs50.4}It's so easy to be a baby human, so you should be one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.33,0:23:08.94,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1\fs50.4}Ababa, ababa! Dance, multiply, and take it to space!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:13.49,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1\fs50.4}To Mars! To Saturn! To the galaxy! Dance! Baby human!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:16.32,ED_rus,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an1}Dance! Baby human!
